Alabama Territory (1818-02-06)

1818/02/06 -> 1819/12/13

TUSCALOOSA created by Alabama Territory from MONTGOMERY and Non-County Area 1; TUSCALOOSA overlapped non-county area in the state of Mississippi.

(Ala. Terr. Acts 1818, 1st sess., secs. 1-3/pp. 16-18)
